-- Merrill's gross CDO exposure is $30 billion
-- 
-- Thu Jan 17, 2008 9:00am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/01/17/us-merrilllynch-cdo-idUSWEN344520080117

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Merrill Lynch & Co Inc on Thursday said its gross exposure to collateralized debt obligations is $30 billion. 

 Merrill executives provided the figure during a conference call. CDOs underpinned by risky subprime mortgages have whipsawed the profits of Merrill and other Wall Street companies. (Reporting by  Tim McLaughlin ; Editing by  Derek Caney )